352
00:23:52,514 --> 00:23:54,766
But no, no way.

353
00:23:55,350 --> 00:23:56,726
<i>I don't believe him.</i>

354
00:23:56,810 --> 00:24:00,147
<i>Clients always lie for their own gain</i>

355
00:24:00,647 --> 00:24:04,442
<i>exaggerating whatever helps them</i>
<i>and burying anything that doesn't.</i>

356
00:24:06,194 --> 00:24:07,737
<i>But there's one thing I'm certain of.</i>

357
00:24:07,821 --> 00:24:08,947
<i>Hey!</i>

358
00:24:09,030 --> 00:24:10,115
NEVER MET A WOMAN LIKE HER

359
00:24:15,162 --> 00:24:17,706
