<i>who's ever called me "hey."</i>

360
00:24:18,832 --> 00:24:22,836
<i>I sat through that drama where you did</i>
<i>all that bad acting, so I know.</i>

361
00:24:22,919 --> 00:24:23,753
- Cute.
<i>- Do Ra-ik.</i>

362
00:24:26,923 --> 00:24:29,801
<i>You could never act this well.</i>

363
00:24:29,885 --> 00:24:31,428
I like you.

364
00:24:34,639 --> 00:24:38,768
